title: Former Marine And Now Special Tactics Officer – Damon Friedman
text:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 2:40:05 — 74.6MB) 
On today’s show: Rhonda Rousey going to the Marine Corps. Ball. Chinese warships spotted in the Bearing Sea during President Obama’s visit to Alaska. JT picks September for the Chairborne Meet UP. Quick ISIS update. Finally Air Force will Test F35 against the A10 in CAS Operations. Invisible drone technology. Oshkosh gets the contract to replace the aging Humvee. Listener Q and A
